{"id":190472,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/10/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-20111020/","date":"2011-10-21T05:31:01Z","modified":"2011-10-21T05:31:01Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐 &#8211; 2011/10/20","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><span> </span><b>(</b></span><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/yigroup\">@yigroup</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/xiaomi2020\">@xiaomi2020</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/10/20/social-media-helps-china-activists-score-victory-for-blind-lawyer/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">社交媒体帮助中国的活动家们为盲人维权律师争取到一个胜利</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——有消息说，临沂警方允许陈光诚的女儿去上学了。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《每日电讯报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/8839235/Chinese-blogger-jailed-for-disrupting-traffic-fails-to-have-sentence-overturned.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">因阻碍交通而入狱的中国博客写手没能推翻原判</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——王荔蕻的遭遇显示出中国政府对于网上活动的惧怕越来越大。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20111020/wl_nm/us_china_tibetans_burnings\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">西藏自焚事件后，中国政府表示将采取严厉措施维护稳定</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——外交部发言人称中国不存在西藏问题，将继续打击民族分裂主义。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-10-20/u-s-urges-china-to-ease-tibet-policy-after-nun-s-immolation.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">西藏尼姑自焚之后，美国呼吁中国放宽西藏政策</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——美国重申中国应尊重人权，特别是西藏人的权利，修正无效的措施。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>NPR</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.npr.org/2011/10/19/141503738/at-105-celebrated-chinese-linguist-now-a-dissident?sc=emaf\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国</span>105<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">岁的语言学家成为政府的批评者</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——发明了汉语拼音的周有光原本可以成为民族英雄，但他在活到</span></span><span><span>100</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">岁之后，却成了政府的眼中钉。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://shadow.foreignpolicy.com/posts/2011/10/19/on_china_its_the_regime_stupid\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">关于中国，最关键的是政权问题</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中美竞争不是国家资本主义能否打败民主资本主义的问题，而是因为中共极力要保住自己的权力。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-10-20/taiwan-s-ma-says-referendum-needed-prior-to-china-peace-talks.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">台湾马英九称在与中国和谈之前，需先举行全民公投</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——此前马表示要在十年内与大陆达成和平协议，被对手蔡英文称此举会威胁到台湾民主</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交学者》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/china-power/2011/10/20/chen-xianmei%E2%80%99s-tragedy/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">陈贤妹的悲剧</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——主动救人的人，却被邻里指责为想要出名挣钱。在一个极端实用主义的国家，很多人甚至不能容忍助人之举。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国见红博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://seeingredinchina.com/2011/10/20/the-good-samaritan-in-china/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的好心人</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——在关于佛山幼童事件的中文报道中，都提到了南京彭宇案。然而那是五年前的案子。一向雷厉风行的政府为何一直未能修改法律鼓励见义勇为？</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【国际外交】</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">国际战略研究所：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.iiss.org/publications/strategic-comments/past-issues/volume-17-2011/august/behind-recent-gunboat-diplomacy-in-the-south-china-sea/?locale=en\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在南中国海炮舰外交的背后</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——自</span></span><span><span>2005</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年以来，南海的局势就趋于紧张。中国近期下水的航母进一步引发周边国家的不安。引发这一切的是能源争夺。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《大西洋》月刊：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.theatlanticwire.com/global/2011/10/libyan-rebels-capture-sirte-qaddafis-hometown/43901/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">利比亚官员称卡扎菲已死</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——对于卡扎菲同志走上死路的详细图文报道。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《时代》周刊：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,2097446,00.html?xid=rss-world&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+time%2Fworld+%28TIME%3A+Top+World+Stories%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">卡扎菲已死，的黎波里的人民欢庆</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——他的下场令人想起当年的墨索里尼。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经济金融】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">皮特森国际经济研究院：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.piie.com/blogs/china/?p=534\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国房地产市场与地方政府财政的联系</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——如果任由房地产泡沫膨胀，整个经济会面临危险；如果过于积极地打击房地产，则地方政府的财政又会出问题</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-10-20/china-to-strictly-control-shadow-banking-risks-liu-says.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">刘明康称中国将严格控制地下金融市场的风险</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国银监会主席刘明康称投资分析家和评级机构低估了中国推进改革的决心和能力</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/10/19/us-china-walmart-idUSTRE79I2PR20111019\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">重庆表示沃尔玛在当地多次违规</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——重庆政府解释为何对沃尔玛采取如此严厉的惩罚措施时，称它一贯逃避责任，有</span></span><span><span>20</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">多次违规记录</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/business/2011/oct/20/china-rare-earth-supplier-suspends-production\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国稀土供应商暂时停产</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——内蒙包钢稀土集团本周宣布停产一个月，希望以此促进稀土价格的回升。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/10/20/twitter-founder-cant-compete-in-china/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">推特创始人称无法进入中国参与竞争</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——杰克・多西很有兴趣与中国的微博一较高下，但是他的产品根本进不了中国</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【生活百态】</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span>CNN</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.cnn.com/2011/10/19/world/china-mother-executed-son/index.html?eref=rss_world&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+rss%2Fcnn_world+%28RSS%3A+World%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">一位母亲为被错杀的儿子争取平反，牵动中国人心</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——</span><span>67</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">岁的农妇张焕枝为了给儿子聂树斌申冤，坚持不懈地到法院上告。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2011/10/19/UFC_fighting_China_cricket\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国绝活儿——斗蟋蟀</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【图说】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<div><i>发送邮件至 yyyyiiii+subscribe@googlegroups.com 即可订阅译文；到iTunes 中搜索“译者”即可订阅和下载译者播客Podcast；点击<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/p/download.html\">这里</a>可以播放和下载所有译者已公开的视频、音频和杂志。（下载需翻墙）。</i><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-6705392560674052743?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":994,"categories":[1],"tags":[12349,9378]}